#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/events/admin.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Any action an admin performs within the admin console can be recorded for auditing purposes.\n"
"The Admin Console performs administrative functions by invoking on the {project_name} REST interface.  {project_name}\n"
"audits these REST invocations.  The resulting events can then be viewed in the Admin Console.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/events/admin.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "To enable auditing of Admin actions, go to the `Events` left menu item and select the `Config` tab.\n"
msgstr ""

